    "expectations and control levels over the emotions of the users, AI-powered chatbots could provide a positive influence on users' emotions 13.",
    "The primary motivation driving this research stems from the growing prevalence and significance of AIpowered chatbots, particularly represented by ChatGPT, in a wide array of applications.",
    "As the deployment of these AI-powered language models becomes increasingly pervasive, it is crucial to comprehensively understand their impact on human-computer interaction experiences 14.",
    "In this context, our study seeks to investigate the specific implications of integrating ChatGPT into an academic research questionnaire, with a particular emphasis on revealing users' emotions and their interactions with AI-powered language model texts and communication.",
